      "rationale": "Eleven constructs assembled from a single certified production lot of 7.5 mm non-cannulated pedicle screws and matching titanium rods. Six constructs tested at Lab A (FDA CDRH), five at Lab B (DePuy Synthes). Lot certificates and assembly records archived. Inter-lab coefficient of variation for stiffness is 4.2%, within acceptable range."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions replicate clinical loading environment across at least two load levels or configurations; ASTM F1717 single-condition testing accepted as minimum but noted as limitation.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 static compression-bending configuration. While this is the regulatory standard, only one load condition is evaluated, limiting the ability to characterize model behavior across the clinical loading envelope. Achieved level is below required; this gap is acknowledged and accepted given the regulatory context and corroborating literature data."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation input parameters (geometry, material, boundary conditions, loading) demonstrably equivalent to experimental conditions; documented mapping table provided.",
      "rationale": "A parameter equivalency table maps each simulation input to its experimental counterpart with traceability to CMM records, material certificates, and test fixture drawings. Boundary condition fidelity confirmed by comparing simulated fixture reaction forces to measured load cell data at sub-yield load levels."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
