      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric E/uval < 1.96 and percentage difference < 10% for all three QoIs; validation uncertainty uval accounts for numerical, experimental, and input uncertainties.",
      "rationale": "E/uval values: stiffness 0.87, yield force 1.12, force at 40 mm 1.34 — all below 1.96 threshold. Percentage differences: stiffness 3.1%, yield force 5.8%, force at 40 mm 7.2% — all below 10% acceptance bound. Validation uncertainty computed per ASME V&V 20 framework. All acceptance criteria met with margin."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
